snippet: Serena Williams advanced to the semifinals of the Western & Southern Open in Mason, Ohio, a tournament she has never won.
abstract: Serena Williams beats Jelena Jankovic, advancing to the semifinals of the Western & Southern Open in Mason, Ohio; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams advanced to the semifinals of the Western & Southern Open in Mason, Ohio, a tournament she has never won.

headline.main: Serena Williams Tops Jankovic to Reach Semifinals
